    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEARCH ALL - CHRISTMAS </h2> is a game in the genre of &quot;hidden object&quot;, in which you need to find all the Christmas candy in the form of a cane (caramel cane) on a large location drawn in the style of &quot;doodling&quot;. The location depicts a winter city. In the foreground of the location is a railway, along which a locomotive periodically passes. Also in the foreground is a carousel with horses, and next to it children are making a snowman. In the middle there is a frozen pond where people are doing their favorite things, someone is skating, and someone is fishing. Between the front layer of the location and the back, there is a huge bridge along the entire settlement. In the background, a viewing wheel rotates and there is a large apartment building.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br>- Animation elements on location;<br>- &quot;Doodling&quot; design style;<br>- 80 caramel canes to find;<br>- Pleasant soundtrack;<br>- Implemented hints! If you find it difficult to find an item, use the hint!<br>- The gameplay can be interrupted at any time, and the game will automatically save the result.",
